snippet.title: Bricky Boy Trailer
snippet.description:
This game is available for free at Play Store: 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.moorlandgames.brickyboy

Bricky Boy is a combination of brick-breaker and pinball genres, represented in a very original style of handheld gaming consoles from the '90s. Combined with a 8-bit soundtrack, this game will let you enjoy the genuine feel of the long-gone gaming computers.

In Bricky Boy you will find lots of entertaining challenges like:

Boss fights,
Quests,
Unique powerup system,
Lots of unlockable skins,
Semi-random generated levels

Get your Bricky Boy and start the adventure!

Read more:
https://moorlandgames.com/bricky-boy/
